&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DFM/DFA Integration:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate with battery design and product engineering teams to optimize designs for manufacturability (DFM) and assembly (DFA) on automated equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Process Optimization:&lt;/strong&gt; Drive continuous improvement for equipment performance, uptime, yield, and cycle time through data analysis, root cause analysis, and robust solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Safety &amp;amp; Compliance:&lt;/strong&gt; Ensure all equipment designs and installations meet safety standards, environmental compliance, and relevant industry regulations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Development:&lt;/strong&gt; Mentor and guide less experienced engineers, fostering technical excellence and continuous learning.&lt;/li&gt;
