&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;3,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;3,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as the central liaison bridging Sales, Service, Parts, Engineering, Operations, and the Dealer Network. Track open action items and orchestrate rapid resolutions for escalated customer concerns.&lt;/p&gt;
