&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with the People Ops and Recruiting teams to ensure we are attracting, retaining, and developing top-tier talent efficiently.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solve business-critical issues by demonstrating extreme ownership and utilizing deep HR expertise to navigate organizational roadblocks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Influence outcomes and drive change management across the organization by building deep trust and relationships with senior leadership on the executive team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a culture of empathy, continuous feedback, and humility, ensuring our teams evolve alongside the business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
