&lt;li&gt;AI-Driven Workflows: Deploy Claude AI Skills and other LLM tools to automate&amp;nbsp;personalized outreach, clean unstructured data, and enhance our internal sales&amp;nbsp;intelligence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The &quot;Source of Truth&quot;: Own the backend architecture. Ensure that Marketing,&amp;nbsp;Sales, and Service Hubs remain aligned through strong operational governance&amp;nbsp;and high standards of data integrity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2. Marketing Attribution &amp;amp; Lifecycle&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full-Funnel Tracking: Build and maintain the infrastructure to track the entire&amp;nbsp;customer journey, from the initial digital touchpoint through vehicle delivery and&amp;nbsp;beyond, while supporting operational workflows across marketing, sales, and&amp;nbsp;dealership onboarding processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ROI Validation: Create the dashboards that prove the ROI of every activation. You&amp;nbsp;must ensure that leadership has a real-time, accurate view of revenue forecasts&amp;nbsp;and marketing spend efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automation &amp;amp; Segments: Design complex email marketing flows and lifecycle&amp;nbsp;automations. You will manage highly targeted segmentation for fleet buyers,&amp;nbsp;partners, and stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3. Sales Enablement &amp;amp; Quote Building&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quote Engineering: Build and maintain the HubSpot Product Library and Quote&amp;nbsp;tool. You will ensure the sales team can generate accurate, branded, and&amp;nbsp;technically sound quotes/contracts instantly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pipeline Excellence: Audit and enforce sales pipeline stages. You are responsible&amp;nbsp;for ensuring that &quot;Deal Stages&quot; are updated correctly and that the system remains&amp;nbsp;highly usable for the sales team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Internal Usability: Conduct ongoing training for internal teams to ensure 100% system adoption and data entry consistency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
