&lt;li&gt;3-4 years of experience in a technical support role, preferably in a Helpdesk or Systems Administrator role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience and well versed with all things Atlassian&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with AV equipment; configuring sound mixers for optimal settings, microphones, speakers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent customer service and communication skills, with the ability to explain technical concepts to non-technical users&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem-solving and troubleshooting skills, with attention to detail and accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of Microsoft Windows operating systems (Windows 10/11) and common desktop applications such as Zoom, Slack, and Microsoft Office.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to lift and move equipment weighing up to 50 lbs unassisted.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice To Have:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
