&lt;li&gt;Experience with Atlassian is a &lt;strong&gt;significant plus&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Certifications relating to Jumpcloud&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Google Workspace experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of consuming and working with APIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with ITIL or other IT service management methodologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
