&lt;li&gt;Certifications such as CCNA, CCNP, CompTIA Network+, or equivalent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with firewall management (Cisco, Palo Alto, Fortinet, or similar) and proficiency in routing protocols such as OSPF, BGP, and EIGRP is expected.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The candidate should have knowledge of switching technologies like VLANs, trunking, and Layer 2 security, along with experience in wireless networking technologies (WPA2, WPA3, 802.11 standards).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with network monitoring tools such as SolarWinds, Nagios, or PRTG, along with experience in multi-ISP management and ensuring redundant internet connectivity through failover and load balancing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with VPNs, network segmentation, and remote access

